{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10108028271844-1":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10108028271844-1","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000673226","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100121273241-1","P_10100121273241-2","P_10100121273241-3","P_10100121273241-4","P_10100121273241-5","P_10100121273241-6","P_10100121273241-7","P_10100121273241-8","P_10100121273241-9","P_10100121273241-10"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":3,"description":"课外阅读","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":1140,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>购买上帝的男孩</strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">①<strong>一个年仅六岁的小男孩（捏着 握着）1美元硬币，沿街一家一家商店地询问：“请问您这儿有上帝卖吗？”</strong>店主要么说没有，要么嫌他在捣乱，不由分说就把他撵出了店门。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">天快黑时，第二十九家商店的店主热情地接待了男孩。老板是个六十多岁的老头，满头银发，慈眉善目。他笑眯眯地问男孩：“告诉我，孩子，你买上帝干嘛？”男孩流着泪告诉老头，他叫邦迪，父母很早就去世了，是被叔叔帕特鲁抚养大的。叔叔是个建筑工人，前不久从脚手架上摔了下来，至今昏迷不醒。医生说，只有上帝才能救他。邦迪想，上帝一定是种非常奇妙的东西，我把上帝买回来，让叔叔吃了，伤就会好。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">老头眼圈也湿润了，问：“你有多少钱？”“1美元。”“孩子，眼下上帝的价格正好是1美元。”老头接过硬币，从货架上拿了瓶“上帝之吻”牌饮料说：“这就是你要找的‘上帝’。”②<strong>邦迪喜出望外，将饮料（捧 抱 包 报）在怀里，兴冲冲地回到了医院。</strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">一进病房，他就开心地叫嚷道　“叔叔　我把上帝买回来了　您很快就会好起来的　”</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">几天后，一个由世界顶尖医学专家组成的医疗小组来到医院，对帕特鲁普进行会诊。他们采用世界最先进的医疗技术，终于治好了帕特鲁普的伤。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">帕特鲁普出院时，看到医疗费账单那个天文数字，差点吓昏过去。可院方告诉他，有个老头帮他把钱全付了。③<strong>那老头是个亿万富翁，从一家跨国公司董事长的位置退下来后，（寄居 隐居）在本市，开了家杂货店打发时光。</strong>那个医疗小组就是老头花重金聘来的。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">帕特鲁普激动不已，他立即和邦迪去感谢老头，可老头已经把杂货店卖掉，出国旅游去了。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">后来，帕特鲁普接到一封信，是那老头写来的，信中说：“年轻人，您能有邦迪这个侄儿，实在是太幸福了，为了救您，他拿一美元到处购买上帝……，感谢上帝，是他挽救了您的生命，但您一定要永远记住，真正的上帝，是人们的爱心！”</p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"<p>根据下面的意思选出文中相应的词语。</p><p>__$$__　指因遇到意外的喜事，心中非常高兴。</p><p>__$$__　形容非常大的数字，已经无法用一个确切的数字来形容。</p>","answers":[{"answer":"1","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[{"id":"KP_10100075277625","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]}],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100003182846","main":1},{"id":"TM_10100000636722","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null},{"answer":"0","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100003182846","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":10,"analysis":"","optionType":"word","options":[{"option":"天文数字","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"喜出望外","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}}],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"beginListenUrl":null,"endListenUrl":null,"scorePercentage":null,"readySeconds":null,"listenFile":null,"contentDesc":null,"answers":null,"voiceTextsNew":null,"jsgf":null,"videoUrl":null,"videoCoverUrl":null,"highlightPos":null},"submitWays":[0],"tags":[101006],"analysisList":null,"pictureUrl":"","extras":{},"tagsDesc":["其他"]},{"content":"<p style=\"white-space: normal;\">给第四自然段选上适当的标点符号。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">一进病房，他就开心地叫嚷道__$$__“叔叔__$$__我把上帝买回来了__$$__您很快就会好起来的__$$__”</p>","answers":[{"answer":"1","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null},{"answer":"2","subAnswers":[],"